{"tid":2311599,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★檢疫中心缺禦寒物資 7旬長者疑冷到病 房內只有「一個枕頭一張被」","createTime":"2020-12-04T07:48:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T08:16:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"637b73f923855a67fa925dfd8f1549703cf23318","tid":2311599,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T07:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XYGT5znpeqlpTzhQVCqL1O3rmtw=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QYBTXTTERJELFPYRK66MH26V7Y.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXYGT5znpeqlpTzhQVCqL1O3rmtw%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQYBTXTTERJELFPYRK66MH26V7Y.jpeg&h=69608789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港昨晚（3日）天氣轉涼，《蘋果》接獲確診者投訴指，其7旬父母和10歲兒子昨日被送往竹篙灣檢疫中心，惟中心沒有足夠枕頭被鋪，暖風機亦短缺，父親被安排獨自一間房，今日起疑不適發燒，暖風機等物資至今仍有待審批送往。確診女兒轟衞生署安排離譜，「係咪應該要確保資源足夠先收人入去？呢個乜嘢政府嚟㗎！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳女士（化名）日前確診入住亞博館社區治療設施，其父母和10歲兒子昨日被安排送往竹篙灣檢疫中心檢疫，惟因中心沒有大房，職員安排其母親與兒子住一間房，父親獨自住另一間。陳女士引述兒子指，房內只有「一個枕頭一張被」，暖風機亦派完；如家屬要送物資入內，需24小時前申請，她批評當局處理離譜，「唔應該將兩個70幾歲擺去『鐵皮屋』，竹篙灣咁凍喎，我爹哋把聲今朝已經唔同咗唔舒服」。其父下午需送往瑪嘉烈醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201204/PLBNEMDUWVDWPPP2UOUDSGX6TQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201204%2FPLBNEMDUWVDWPPP2UOUDSGX6TQ%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGG%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=4dfedbe7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201204%2FPLBNEMDUWVDWPPP2UOUDSGX6TQ%2F&h=d7c23350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201204/PLBNEMDUWVDWPPP2UOUDSGX6TQ/</a>"},{"pid":"3e3ed9d0811873d8b6916cb7cb95d3cddd2f1809","tid":2311599,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T07:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" cl